#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:14
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_START_TARTARUS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:20
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TEXT_START_TARTARUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The jump into Tartarus was long and difficult, seeming to take ages. What "
"you see on the other end of your journey can only be described as... "
"bizarre. Multiple blue stars surround you in a perfectly circular pattern, "
"but they seem to emit no discernible signs of radiation. Your comms struggle"
" under the might of thousands of hails from all directions, all points in "
"space and time, being sent every second, their contents being only horrific "
"screams and pleas for help. You decide to mute the ship's radio, an act "
"which notably takes several attempts."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:41
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems even this supernatural slug gel is unable to hold the ship together"
" after this much punishment. Everything has its limits after all."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:43
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:48
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The old Slug king is a surprisingly powerful fighter for someone who died "
"from eating poisoned melons. Still, it seems even ghosts can't stop your "
"crew's prowess."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:50
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:57
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"After figuring out where you are and what you're here to do, you check your list of bounties. Six of the seven entries have been mysteriously populated with information, with the seventh remaining blank. With no other leads, you begin to parse the document, revealing your first target: Slimer, the long-dead spirit of a Slug king.\n"
"\n"
"\tSlimer was known throughout the Multiverse as the biggest glutton there ever was, a fact that they wore proudly. They were laid low by a batch of hallucinogenic melons, sending them into a deep coma from which they never recovered. Nobody chose to help them, on account of how rude, selfish, and vengeful Slimer could be in life. As you finish reading the entry, you look up to see a gigantic vessel out of the viewport, composed entirely out of Slug repair gel!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:64
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Hail the vessel."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:66
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide to turn your comms back on, praying the voices would no longer "
"haunt you. To your surprise, only sweet silence lies on the other end, "
"though the view on your screen is... rather concerning. A luminous figure in"
" the shape of a filthy, yet exquisitely-dressed Slug stares back, in an "
"almost trance-like haze. You knew the Spook Chasers said these guys were "
"indeed the souls of the dead, but you couldn't possibly have expected them "
"to be right after all!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:68
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Slimer...?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:70
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The vibrant green spirit begins to jump up and down, as if they were a child"
" in a candy store, and emits a form of preternatural screeching that your "
"translator can barely keep up with. \"...hun... gry... I must... f-food! "
"Food! I haven't... had food for... f-for centuries!\" The feed cuts before "
"you can even respond, and you hear the sound of a teleporter locking onto "
"your ship. Battle stations!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:73
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:79
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_gozer\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Goziodeon) \"Who are you pretenders?! We are the only Rivals to the Spook "
"Chasers in this town! Scram!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:81
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_gozer\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Slug simply chuckles, briefly breaking out of their starving daze, "
"before emitting a form of preternatural screeching that your translator can "
"barely keep up with. \"...hugh-... y-your little... organization meansss... "
"nothing here! I will... I will do my master a favor and... devour your "
"little gassseousss body!\" The feed cuts before you can even respond, and "
"you hear the sound of a teleporter locking onto your ship. Battle stations!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:84
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_1\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_gozer\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:94
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"After a grueling battle, the gelatinous vessel has finally met its fate. You"
" can only hope its captain's spirit has been put to rest in the process, as "
"you sift through the wreckage for valuable scrap metals."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:98
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:100
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you prepare to jump to your next target, Slimer manifests himself aboard your ship. With guns pointing from every crewmember, the ancient king surrounded, he speaks. \"...you... Y-you ended... h-hunger!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tYour crew drop their blasters as the Slug raises their empty hands. \"Oh... oh, glorious savior! You are truly... a kind heart beyond me! The spell, it binds me. I cannot help now, but... I will see what I can do, savior!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe next bounty seems to warn you that the target will be immune to ion damage."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:113
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Shell vessel splits into several pieces, the energy racing along its "
"hull fading into nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:115
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:120
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The shell might have been cracking with ion, but at the end of the day no "
"shell can withstand concentrated fire forever."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:122
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:129
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Next up on the shopping list, is Phys. According to your bounty list, she was a Shell who suffered from a cocktail of congenital diseases. The scientists in charge of her birth didn't want to give up on her, seeing her illness as a challenge to be overcome. So, to keep her heart at a steady rhythm, they infused her body with electric power.\n"
"\n"
"\tWhile her physical form may have been spared, the pain of the process drove Phys mad, causing the Shell to enter a rampage throughout the breeding facility. Mere minutes of life were cut short when the local security team was forced to gun her down. Her soul can no longer move on, not with the excruciating suffering still coursing through her very being."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:133
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_2\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:135
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_2\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you finish reading her bounty, you spot your target already "
"barreling towards you. Cyan power crackles along the ship's hull, arcing "
"electricity obliterating nearby chunks of debris as the vessel moves into "
"attack position, refusing all hails. Prepare for battle!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:138
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_2\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:146
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_PHYS_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Shell vessel splits into several pieces, the energy racing along its "
"hull fading into nothing. You wonder if there were others like Phys, victims"
" of the Shells trying a little too hard."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:150
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_PHYS_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:152
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_PHYS_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your train of thought is interrupted by Phys manifesting directly on your bridge, just as Slimer did earlier, and you get a good look at her for the first time. The ghost is on the smaller side, with several cracks running down her shell, all pulsating with electricity as she tilts to the side.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"You... s-save friend! Help... save thhhhhhe othhhhhers!\" Phys' voice is filled with static, and her speech is very crude, but you do get an idea of what she's imploring you to do before she fades away... if you could save Slimer and Phys from this, then maybe the other souls could be saved!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:163
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty Mantis ship cracks apart before exploding, another fiery blaze "
"that consumes the poor ghost."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:165
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:170
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Aleenor was certainly one of the mightiest opponents you have ever faced. "
"Maybe you can find some kind of momento to show the Mantis Queen later as "
"proof of your victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:172
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:179
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Knowing your next target will likely be just as hostile at first sight, you ready your ship before reading the next entry. Aleenor, a legendary Bishop of the Mantis Hive, revered even amongst her peers and her enemies as one of the most skilled and dangerous hunters in the Multiverse.\n"
"\n"
"\tSomething sticks out to you - her bounty does not make any mention of trauma or unfinished business that could potentially lead her to linger after death. As you close your third bounty, you find both your FTL and Multiverse drives are on the fritz, trapping you at the beacon! It seems you're in too deep to turn back now..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:183
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_3\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:185
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_3\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Aleenor's vessel does not appear immediately to you, and you have to chase "
"the bright pink vessel down, forcing the Bishop to hail. \"Ah, a "
"Renegade...! I hoping not to see you, on... important mission! Given by "
"Queen...\" She pauses for a second, as if struggling to remember. "
"\"...Queen... Queen Latrakkpkat! Yes, important mission indeed! Sorry in "
"advance. Don't have time to spare!\" Her weapons power on, and any further "
"attempts to hail her are met with radio silence."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:188
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_3\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:196
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Bishops are truly formidable, especially this one, but you manage to "
"triumph. Violet pheromones and scintillating pieces of room spread out into "
"space."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:200
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:202
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You brace yourself for another manifestation, seeing as how the last two appeared to you following combat. Like clockwork, the Mantis appears on your bridge, her expression one of... relief.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"Kind soul...! I hear stories about how formidable Renegades can be, and... it warms heart to know I wasn't misled.\" She is oddly fluent in your tongue, which helps ease communication. \"If... you have question, I can answer about me! Though... I am bound to stay silent about Tartarus... a foul necromantic spell, from one who saved me.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:206
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Who are you, exactly?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:208
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Mantis bows to you with great pride. \"My name is Aleenor Lakitrapikk. "
"Before death, I serve Queen Latrakkpkat, the greatest Queen to grace our "
"empire! In the Hive, I made my home... I must have raised and trained "
"thousands of Mantis, most of which eventually become Suzerain!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:210
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "How did you end up like this?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:212
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Aleenor's pride vanishes in an instant, replaced by a sensation of grief. "
"\"I died as I lived. Protecting eggs, and hatchlings! Incubators failed, "
"make fire in the chamber, and... well, Mantis claw not meant to hold fire "
"extinguisher. There not enough time to save both me and them... so, I chose "
"them.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:214
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "My condolences."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:216
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Bishop simply smiles and nods, speaking with an eerie amount of "
"literacy. \"We all must die someday, Renegade. I am simply happy my death "
"wasn't for nothing. Regardless... you have aid from me when you need! Can't "
"tell when your journey will end, but... I want to be with you when it "
"does.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:231
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The lava filled ship suddunly releases a mighty explodion on its central "
"wing, and just like that, all the lava instantly loses all heat."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:233
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:238
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Vin might have looked unkillable, but his size and regeneration abilities "
"were clearly no match for your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:240
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:247
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_4\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You prepare your ship for combat as you jump towards your next target, thinking over what Aleenor said about a \"necromantic spell\", and what Phys said about \"saving friends\". Perhaps these lost souls... aren't here by choice? Whatever is forcing them to hold on must be here somewhere.\n"
"\n"
"\tNext up on the chopping block is Vin, a Paladin in service of the ever-so-stalwart Theocracy. Apparently, his death came when he forgot to turn off his ship's autopilot before going to bed, sending his vessel careening into the local sun. Understandably, such a death was something he'd probably be mad at."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:251
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_4\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Well, that isn't disturbing at all."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:253
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_4\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As usual, once you finish reading your entry, you spot a fearsome Rock "
"vessel in front of you, its armor plates glowing as if they were made of "
"lava. Its weapons are ablaze, and its comms are silent. No time to waste on "
"formalities!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:256
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_4\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:264
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_VIN_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Next verse, same as the first. Another mighty ship taken down and another "
"soul freed from whoever is keeping them here."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:268
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_VIN_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:270
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_VIN_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"This time, you don't even need to wait for Vin to show up; he's already in your quarters when you return for a short rest. With one arm, he immediately pins you to the wall, scowling out a message as a long, luminous crack down his left eye burns itself into your vision.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"Federation dog. I do not care about your mission, or your cause. All I care about is kicking the teeth out of that Crystal-damned necromancer keeping all of us trapped under her finger. So, I will remain close until the deed is done - or, until you die, leaving me free to commandeer your ship, whichever comes first. Then, I will accompany you to the end of your pathetic little errand, if only because it is a fair trade. Understood?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tYou nod, Vin grins and lets go of you, leaving the room as he speaks \"Good, now get back to work, this ship isn't going to fly itself\"."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:283
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship crumbles to pieces, with the cargo bay causing almost a hundred "
"drones to tumble out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:285
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:290
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Cleo's connection and dominion over his drones was a sight to behold, you "
"wonder if he would have been a better engineer instead."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:292
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:302
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_5\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the stars swirl outside during your FTL jump, your mind races with the possibilities of who this necromancer could be. Why... and, how, did she summon the spirits of the dead? Is she just as much a victim of something as they are? You have to put your thinking on hold for a moment, for your fifth target is ready.\n"
"\n"
"\tAccording to your handy ghost guide, this is Cleo, an MFK Ace in life. He developed a love of all things drone and automated in his time with the Rebellion, which made it all the more ironic when he was tortured to death by a modified repair drone. Now, it is said that he has developed a form of Stockholm syndrome, despising all flesh-and-blood life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:306
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_5\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:308
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_5\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Just as you expected, Cleo's vessel is ready for you. A powerful Rebel ship,"
" painted in dark blue colors with an ethereal pattern shimmering across its "
"surface, lies in wait, ready to strike."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_5\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:319
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_CLEO_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship crumbles to pieces, with the cargo bay causing almost a hundred "
"drones to tumble out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:324
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_CLEO_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:326
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_CLEO_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You wait for a long time, but... Cleo never appears. However, as you rest in"
" your quarters, a small slip of paper ejects itself from the vent cover, "
"with a hastily scribbled note on it. \"stay out of the maintenance closet "
"and we won't have a problem\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:335
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The golden plate of the ship were no match for your weapons, it's a shame "
"its powerful beam pierce technology didn't survive the fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:337
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:342
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Even though the ship looks like it could take quite a bit more punishment, "
"it suddunly colapses in on itself, taking Zulu out with it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:344
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:351
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_6\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can even reflect on this jump, or check your bounties, your "
"entire command center is flooded by a golden light, and a Lanius vessel "
"makes itself known. Its hail somehow forces its way into your feed, the "
"usual static of an empty call in Tartarus being replaced with golden "
"religious symbols and frightening imagery flashing in sequence. On the other"
" end of the forced call is a shining, golden Lanius Welder, standing proud "
"like some sort of knight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:354
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_6\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:356
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_6\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Welder speaks in an imperious tone, voice booming through the speakers. \"Ah, so YOU'RE the little meat-puppet who's been causing us so much trouble! Slimer, that gluttonous idiot, was supposed to devour every trace of you, but I guess he wasn't enough for you. The fact that you are here now both impresses and disgusts me!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tAngrily eyeing you up and down, they continue. \"Your vessel is nothing to scoff at, but... in the name of, and at the command of G, our lord and savior, I shall smite you down! Have at thee, brigand!\" The vessel cuts comms, rather rudely, and rushes into battle."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:361
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_BOUNTIES_6\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:369
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Even though the battle took a few minutes at most, around you it seems as if"
" several eons have passed. Stars have appeared where there were none, and "
"others have transformed into dwarves, nebulas, or vanished entirely."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:373
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:375
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Shortly after the glimmering pieces of the vessel drift away, they disappear entirely. In a blinding flash of light, the entire ship reappears without a scratch! Before you can even try to figure out how to defeat such a foe, however, its weapons fold back into the hull, and the Welder holds a hand up to silence the discussion.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"Captain.\" His tone, all of a sudden, is soft, almost fatherly - very different from the initial encounter. \"I understand you may be alarmed by what just happened, and so may your valiant crew! But... I simply ask you to stay for a moment, to let me explain why I'm here and... and what happened.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:379
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, what's going on here?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:381
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Lanius contemplates for a moment, weighing his options. \"My name is "
"Zulu. I know, it's not a normal name for a Lanius. Though... it's more of a "
"nickname, given to me by the one behind all of... this.\" Zulu frowns and "
"looks to the side, remembering several things that you can't quite figure "
"out. \"Technically speaking... all of this is actually my fault, I'm afraid."
" My death is, sadly, what started this entire operation. Though... "
"unfortunately, I can't exactly elaborate more right now, since... I'm bound "
"not to speak of it.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:383
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "So you can't give me actual answers?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:385
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Sadly, not yet. But... I can say that the end of your journey is near. You"
" will very soon meet the one who did this to all of us, the one who's "
"tortured so many souls within Tartarus. I want to be there when it happens, "
"so... please, let me come with you! Let me join the souls following you "
"through space and time.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:387
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "It would be an honor, Zulu."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:389
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_ZULU_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Excellent.\" The Welder nods, their form dissipating as the other souls "
"whisper words of joy around you. \"Your final bounty can only be read at the"
" exit... she cannot conceal herself if you're close to her.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:404
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"While the energy shield was a powerful threat, the ship's actual hull was "
"quite fragile. For as neurotic as G was, she seemed to overlook key "
"weaknesses to her design."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:406
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:411
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As G died, a massive explosion ruptures through the ship. Your crew has "
"barely enough time to escape before the hull looks like its about to combust"
" completely."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:413
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:422
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DEATH_G\"]/lose/@text"
msgstr ""
"With your Multiverse drive in tow, G is able to finally complete her plan. "
"The Multiverse will soon know true fear."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:430
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"Location of the final bounty, it seems to only be available after all the "
"other bounties are done first."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:431
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the final bounty."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:433
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The space here is extremely quiet. No lights, no movement. There's not even "
"a jump beacon here, though you can still somehow jump here."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:436
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We have work to do still."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:440
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_bounty_progression\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The seventh bounty entry is empty. The rest of the list must be cleared "
"first!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:444
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS\"]/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_bounty_progression\""
" and @lvl=\"6\"]/text"
msgstr "Read the final bounty."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:450
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you open your bounty list, you find the seventh entry is no longer "
"corrupted. Opening it, however, reveals something... concerning. The entire "
"file is promptly overwritten with thousands of unreadable characters, with "
"vague threats and depictions of unspeakable acts interspersed through the "
"noise. Your head begins to hurt looking at it all, crushing migraines "
"pushing themselves into your perception."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:452
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:454
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Space and time themselves begin to fold and stretch around you as crimson light begins to fill the empty stretch of existence your vessel finds itself in. A gigantic vessel composed of black cubes with faded, red edges, partially phased out of this realm of existence, begins to manifest. Every speaker on your ship begins to emit an earsplitting hiss, interspersed with the cries of the damned, pleas for help, shouts of rage. The sounds, and every screen on your ship, are all shot through with one word, which imprints itself into your very mind just by looking at it.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"BEG.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:460
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Beg."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:462
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You drop to your knees, begging for it to stop. As your crew follow suit, the maddening stimulus subsides, revealing a cube-shaped alien on your viewscreen. Her single eye stares into your very being, as if her gaze was a thousand knives driven into your heart, and she speaks in a commanding, yet melancholic tone.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\"It seems you've finally found who you're looking for. How... quaint! To be frank, I expected a foe far more impressive than... this. I've spent eons thinking about what my final showdown would look like, and I've always wanted it to be something... climactic. Another Royal? A Crystalline queen? Perhaps the Lanius King himself, so ancient as he is. It seems, however... that I'm... stuck with you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:466
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"\"G... Please, you must stop all this, allow this mortal to free you from "
"your curse, please!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:468
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Zulu manifests himself on your bridge, to everyone's surprise. G stops for a moment, before turning to address the Lanius, the weight of a million stars lifted off of your shoulders as G turns her gaze from you. \"I'm... I'm sorry, old friend. The force that compels me is greater than any of us, or all of us combined... but at least, you have recovered your mind.\" The alien turns back to you, the crushing gaze making you drop to your knees. \"You, Renegade... you will not be so lucky.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tZulu attempts to continue speaking, but G cuts him off. \"Oh, Zulu... I know you are trying to help, but... this battle is inevitable. That god-forsaken book compels me to fight! I promise... when this battle is over, I promise I will bring you right back, all over again.\" G cuts the feed, her immense vessel roaring to life as the mere activation of its engines sends ripples through the fabric of reality."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:474
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_FINAL_BOSS_TRUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:486
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"G's ship fights to the bitter end, and it couldn't have been more of a "
"climactic exit. As you land the final shot to its oddly fragile hull, the "
"chipped, broken cubes collapse into themselves, the entire ship folding into"
" a singularity before exploding in a flash of light that threatens to shred "
"your retinas. By the time the smoke clears, the fragments of her ship are "
"visible again, a million tiny shards of tech you don't recognize. Finally..."
" you've won."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:493
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:495
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You look around, the souls you've freed manifesting one by one, all of you waiting for G to appear. After a long, tense pause, the cube-shaped entity manifests herself aboard your vessel.\n"
"\t\t\t      \n"
"\t\t\t\"It seems... what I most feared has come true. And it wasn't soon enough, though... I'm glad it ended this way, instead of the millions of other ways it could have...\" G turns to Zulu, hovering in place.\n"
"\t\t\t\t  \n"
"\t\t\t\"Zulu... no, everyone. I'm sorry. I am so, so sorry. I... I understand if you can't forgive me for what I've done to you all...\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:502
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Eh, you gave us a lot of scrap. Can't go wrong with that."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:504
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The room falls utterly silent. The Revenants all look to each other, then to you, then to G, wanting to speak about this bizarre matter.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPhys is the first to speak, ever so chipper after you freed her from her pain. \"Big cube brought Phys back... Phys happy! Phys very happy, can... can live! Live again!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSlimer shrugs, assuming a casual demeanor. \"Eh, you gave me another ssssshot at life... or, un-life, I guesssss... and, without hunger plaguing me every waking hour. All good in my book.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAleenor ponders aloud. \"What you did is barbaric, and... and cruel... just like Mantis. G, you make me proud!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCleo is huddled in the corner of a nearby room, surrounded by drone parts, a thousand-yard stare leveled at everyone in the room. \"Don't... d-don't come near my drones, any of you!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tVin is, understandably, very upset, having to physically restrain himself from striking G. \"I'm... I'm outnumbered! Bah... fine. You get to live another day, you filthy brick. But if I EVER lay my eyes on you again... I will rip you limb from limb, until there is nothing left of you to bury.\" He stomps out of the room.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFinally, Zulu chimes in, his words causing G to turn away with a mixture of joy and mild embarrassment. \"Oh, how could I ever be mad at you, dear friend...? You went through so much trouble to bring me back, to bring us all back...\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWith the whole crowd having said what they wanted to say to G, everyone turns to you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:520
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "We still have a mission. Tag along, if you like!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:522
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_G_DEFEAT\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The cube stares at you, rather shocked and befuddled. \"After... after all "
"of this, after eons of what I've done, you... still want to work with me? "
"I'm... impressed. Flabbergasted, even. Well... I'll have an exit plan drawn "
"up in just a moment. Thank you... Captain.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:536
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_G_SECTOR_SELECT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You inform G that you are ready, to which she responds by nodding enthusiastically. \n"
"\n"
"\t\"Before I followed the dark path of necromancy, I was the Royal Navigator of the Obelisk Empire. I charted out every hyperspace lane, every optimal beacon position, every Multiversal tunnel... I even discovered the cluster phenomenon!\" G's pride swells, and she tilts upwards. \"My greatest invention, however... was the waystone. A way to reach anywhere, any time, regardless of your fuel, or your FTL drive's capabilities. Sadly, I was dragged into this whole mess before I could inform Queen Y, and only had time to make a single waystone... which I now entrust to you.\" G places a perfectly cubical device, brimming with fuchsia light, into your hands.\n"
"\n"
"\t\"This is how we will leave this cursed place. Just set a destination in your navigation system and leave the waystone next to your engines... it'll do all the work for you!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:542
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_G_SECTOR_SELECT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Thank you, G."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:544
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_G_SECTOR_SELECT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"Don't worry about it... savior. It's the least I could do.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:546
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_G_SECTOR_SELECT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Let's get out of here."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:554
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, one final thing! Before you go, there's another token of gratitude I "
"would like you to see... I've been hoarding a collection of weapons from my "
"dear friends, and... I'll let you keep the one you like the most! That, "
"and... I'll see what I can do to set all of them free."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:556
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pick Slimer's bomb launcher."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:558
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Slimer grins. \"You want my bomb launcher...? Well... guesssss I hope it'll "
"ssssserve you jussssst asssss well asssss it did me.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:561
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:567
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Pick Phys' beam."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:569
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Phys rocks from side to side, ecstatic. \"My beam! Very powerful, very "
"shiny! Very... zappy!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:572
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:578
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Pick Aleenor's laser."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:580
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_SELECT_TARTARUS\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "Aleenor waves. \"The truest weapon of war. Everyone die in one shot!\""

