#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1220
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"There's nothing here, not even a star in sight. You sigh as you stare out "
"into the void, simply waiting to see how this whole G thing will turn out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1221
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"The infinite blackness of space stretches as far as you can see in all "
"directions. There is no sound out there, not even background noise on your "
"comms."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1222
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"For a second, you feel like you are being watched. You, of course, see "
"nothing when you turn around, but you keep an eye out just in case."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1223
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"The complete lack of anything material in your ship's general vicinity puts "
"you on edge. You half expect stars, nebulae, perhaps even Rebel chatter... "
"but there isn't even a fleet to worry about here."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1228
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1245
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty golden ship cracks and splinters, its own massive weight causing "
"it to colapse in on itself."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1247
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Phantoms are normally not well versed in crew combat, their speciality is "
"sabotage after all. But somehow, through their own greed, Augustus was able "
"to overcome that issue and put up a really rough fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1266
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the spot specified by the urn. As expected, a vessel of unique design orbits the beacon, hailing you the moment it senses your presence. The ship's hull appears to be made entirely out of gold; rumor has it a ship like this belonged only to the richest Phantom to ever live. Augustus, slain by mutiny, the ghost of a Ghost with the most.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\"Hark, pray to the lords that you evacuate with haste! Elsewise thine vessel's rust and decay might erode mine own's most invaluable shine! Shall thou refuse to meet my demands, expect a most swift death of peculiar means... For I shall dismantle thine hull with projectiles of solid gold, salvage the remains, and become even richer!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1273
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Prepare to fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1275
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Realizing there's no way out of here without a fight, you turn on your "
"weapons and engage the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1277
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1285
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're also surprised to find a special weapon among the wreckage! You've never seen anything even remotely close to something like this before, so you assume it must be a custom model made by the strange beings.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tIn addition, someone who appears to be the same person you just killed appears aboard your ship, fading into existence. Before you can fire upon him, he swears loyalty, praising you for freeing him from his \"captor\", apparently an impostor."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1289
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_DEFEAT\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "Augustus"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1304
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The spider-like ship crumbles and stops responding shortly after. You are "
"glad you don't have arachnophobia otherwise this fight would be a lot "
"harder..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1306
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Spiders are tough oponents, their relative small size hiding fierce combat "
"potential. While sally seemed to be more of a support unit, she wasn't the "
"easiest to kill either."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1313
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1325
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the spot specified by the urn. As expected, a vessel of unique design orbits the beacon, hailing you the moment it senses your presence. The ship's hull seems to mostly be composed of flesh, matching old tales of a scientist who fused themselves with their pet spider in order to save their own life.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\"Oh my stars! If it isn't a new friend! Now, please don't be upset, dear, but a force beyond my control command I fight you! Quite unfortunate for you, but at least I promise you... I will keep you company in the afterlife, you are my new friend after all!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1331
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Prepare to fight!"

