#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1343
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're also surprised to find a special weapon among the wreckage! You've never seen anything even remotely close to something like this before, so you assume it must be a custom model made by the strange beings.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tIn addition, someone who appears to be the same person you just killed appears aboard your ship, fading into existence. Before you can fire upon them, they swear loyalty, praising you for freeing them from their \"captor\", apparently an impostor."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1347
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY_DEFEAT\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "Sally"
